reviewText: Hilarious and smart, great experience for people who like Euro Cinema. It definitely carries the spirit and the more down to Earth feel of an old, non-Hollywood movie. Would love to watch it few million times more, even though it is as old as I am.
One of the may funny Italian movies I have had a pleasure to view, containing sophisticated level of hummer portrayed that people do not want to grow old, but simply hold on to there youth.
